    "descriptionPlain": "Gluten-Free, Low-Calorie Dinner | Healthy Veg Dimsum Recipe by Balance Nutrition\n\nCraving your favorite comfort food but scared that dieting means giving it up?\nThink again! 💚\n\nAt Balance Nutrition, all our clients enjoy every cuisine, Thai, Chinese, Italian & more, while staying on track with their goals. With 1400+ healthy recipes and a complete restaurant guide, eating well has never been this easy (or delicious!).\n\nToday’s Recipe: Low-Calorie Gluten-Free Veg Dimsums\n\nIngredients:\nCarrot (finely chopped) - 1 no.\nMushroom (finely chopped) - 3 no.\nSpring onion - 1 spring\nGarlic - 1 clove\nSoy sauce - 1 tbsp\nVinegar - 1 tsp\nBrown rice - 1 katori\nLettuce leaves - 3 no.\n\nDirections:\n1️⃣ Finely chop all the veggies and mix them with soy sauce, vinegar, and cooked brown rice.\n2️⃣ Place a small portion of the filling in lettuce leaves and fold like dim sums.\n3️⃣ Steam for 5–7 minutes and serve hot!\n\nThis recipe is:\n✅ Gluten-Free\n✅ Low in Calories\n✅ High in Fiber\n✅ Packed with Asian Flavors\n\nWatch the full video to see how it’s done and enjoy guilt-free dining that actually tastes amazing!",
