    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "The 9-Calorie Noodles You’ll FALL IN LOVE With! Zero Fat, Low Carb, Guilt-Free Recipe \n\nYes, you heard that right, Shirataki noodles have only 9 calories per 100 grams!\nThey’re fat-free, low-carb, and absolutely perfect for your weight-loss journey.\n\nHere’s how to make this delicious and healthy bowl in minutes \n\nIngredients:\nMixed Vegetables (Carrot, Cabbage, Spring Onion, etc.)\nOil – ½ tsp\nVinegar – 1 tsp\nSoya Sauce – 1 tsp\nShirataki Noodles – 1 katori\nSchezwan Sauce – ½ tsp\nSalt – to taste\nPepper Powder – ¼ tsp\n\nMethod:\n1️⃣ Heat a little oil in a pan.\n2️⃣ Sauté your veggies.\n3️⃣ Add vinegar and soya sauce.\n4️⃣ Mix in a touch of Schezwan sauce for flavor.\n5️⃣ Add the Shirataki noodles and a little water.\n6️⃣ Boil until it reaches your perfect consistency.\n7️⃣ Garnish with lettuce, corn, or your favorite toppings! \n\nEnjoy this guilt-free, filling, and super tasty meal that supports your fitness goals!",
