    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Could you have inflammation?\n\nThen you’ll have to read this.\n\nAfter almost seven months of research by Khyati & our R&D team, we are thrilled to offer ADVANCED versions of two of our most successful online diet programs.\n\nThis journey began when Ma’am turned 40 last year and noticed sudden changes in her mood, bloating, periods, and even body fat.\n\nWith her adenomyosis (a type of endometriosis), things just went downhill. This led us, dietitians at Balance Nutrition, to start studying the impact of inflammation in women and men over 30.\n\nWe researched the effects of gluten, dairy, stress, and packaged foods on individuals experiencing inflammation due to health issues.\n\nAlthough our diets have always been naturally anti-inflammatory, we have now developed 'Intermittent Fasting Advanced' & 'Plateau Breaker Advanced', focusing primarily on addressing the core of the problem.\n\nKey Features\n✔ Anti-inflammatory diets designed to combat inflammation\n✔ Available only in 90-day & 180-day formats\n✔ Specifically tailored to address inflammation\n✔ Incorporates anti-inflammatory foods easily available in your kitchen\n✔ Includes gluten-free, lactose-free, and vegan meal ideas based on client suitability",
