    "descriptionPlain": "To know more about our online diet program and how we work, contact Krishna at +917021960648\n\n probably seen it everywhere: “Eat more protein if you want to lose weight after 40.”\nSo you added protein powders, shakes, protein bars… but still facing the same issues:\n❌ No inch loss\n❌ Weight stuck\n❌ Cravings won’t go away\n\nHere’s the truth: After working with 1000s of women, I can confidently say that fat loss is not just about eating more protein.\nIt’s about understanding your body, fixing hormonal imbalances, and addressing the root cause, inflammation.\n\nIn fact, suddenly jumping to a high-protein diet + aggressive workouts can actually worsen inflammation… leading to bloating, weight gain, and digestive issues.\n\nSo what works instead?\n\n✅ Cooked, not raw: Skip raw salads & excess fruits. Focus on cooked veggies, well-cooked millets & probiotic-rich curd.\n✅ Healing spices: Jeera, turmeric, pepper & fennel seeds, taken with hot water, are natural anti-inflammatory boosters.\n✅ Rest over overtraining: HIIT & heavy workouts stress the body. Rest + recovery help it heal.\n✅ Fix your sleep: Deep sleep is the most underrated weight loss tool. It resets hormones and supports fat loss naturally.\n\nIf you want to know how to structure your meals for fat loss in your 40s and beyond, drop a “BALANCE” in the comments or check out our program link in the description.",
