    "descriptionPlain": "To know more about our online diet program and how we work, contact:\nBarkha – +91 9152419848\n\nDiet Tips for a Perfect Karva Chauth Vrat! \n\nComment “Fast” if you want to lose 5kg before Diwali!\n\nWant to make your fast easier and more energizing? Follow this smart nutrient sequence! \n\nPre-Fast [Sargi]\n-Coconut water - keeps you hydrated and replenishes electrolytes.\n-Hydrating fruits - watermelon, orange, apple, fiber, water, and potassium to keep energy steady.\n-Healthy fats - 2 walnuts or 3–4 almonds to keep you full.\n-Protein - helps preserve muscle and sustain energy.\n-Carbs last - mindfully load up for the day ahead.\n\nAfter the Fast\n-coconut water - to prevent headaches.\n-Follow with a date - gentle energy boost.\n-Then enjoy a balanced meal with fiber and protein to stabilize blood sugar.\n-Avoid overeating - large meals can overwhelm your digestive system.\n\nWhy it matters: Eating in the right order keeps your energy steady, prevents fatigue, and protects your muscles.",
