    "id": "1639",
    "title": "What Happens When You STOP Eating Fake HEALTHY FOODS for 30 Days #balancenutrition #weightloss",
    "category": "General",
    "subType": "Gyan",
    "mediaType": "reel",
    "videoUrl": null,
    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "What Happens When You STOP Eating Fake HEALTHY FOODS for 30 Days\n\nTo know more about our online diet program and how we work, contact:\nBarkha – +91 9152419848\n\nAs a nutritionist who lost 40 kg and has maintained it for the last 10 years, I’ve seen both, the struggles and the success.\n\nLosing weight is hard… but you know what’s harder?\nGetting sick because of the “healthy” foods we’re told to eat!\n\nAfter years of learning, I discovered that these 5 foods were silently blocking my progress and slowing my metabolism.\n\nHere’s what I stopped eating completely:\n1️⃣ Peanut Butter – High in fat & calories; 2 tbsp = ~190 kcal\n2️⃣ Granola – Loaded with sugar & fats; 1 cup = ~450 kcal\n3️⃣ Fruit Juice – Full of sugar, no fiber; 1 cup = ~120 kcal\n4️⃣ Diet Snacks – Hidden sugars, unhealthy fats; ~150 kcal per serving\n5️⃣ White Bread – Low fiber, spikes sugar; 2 slices = ~140 kcal\n\nThese look healthy, but aren’t helping your body or hormones!\n\nBacked by science and my personal experience, making this one change helped me sustain my 40 kg weight loss and feel stronger every day.\n\nComment “HEALTHY” if you want me to share what I replaced these with!\n\n(Healthy Food Myths, Nutrition Tips, Calorie Awareness, Weight Loss India, Nutritionist Advice, Fat Loss Journey, Balanced Nutrition, Smart Eating Habits, Energy Boost, Overeating, Fiber-Rich Foods, Sustainable Weight Loss)",
    "tags": [],
