    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Exercise alone won’t help you lose weight!\n\nAs much as we dislike hearing this, it’s a fact.\n\nAt Balance Nutrition, we know that the key to effective weight loss starts with your meals. You could exercise for two hours every day, but without the right diet, results will be hard to come by.\n\nThat’s why we focus on correcting your diet with concepts like invisible calories, hidden calories, negative calories, and smart meal planning principles that make all the difference.",
