    "videoUrl": null,
    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Suhoor doesn’t have to be a struggle!\n\nIn my recent podcast with The Fat Kid Show, I shared how to build the perfect Suhoor meal to keep you full, energized, and craving-free throughout the day. \n\nNo more post-Suhoor bloating—just the right fuel for your fast!\n\n💡 Here’s what works best:\n✅ High-fiber + high-protein = Long-lasting energy\n✅ Swap oily parathas for multigrain roti + egg whites\n✅ Hydrate smartly & balance your plate for sustained energy\n\nA well-planned Suhoor makes all the difference! Save this for Ramadan & tag someone who needs this! ✨",
