    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "At Balance Nutrition, we’ve always believed that your health journey should work with your lifestyle not against it.\n\nAnd let’s be honest saying goodbye to restaurant food forever? Not happening. \n\nThat’s exactly what our founder & chief nutritionist Khyati Rupani felt when she started her own transformation journey. So instead of cutting out her favorite Saturday outings, she began writing down:\n 📒 What she ate\n 🧠 How it made her feel\n 📈 What worked (and what didn’t)\n\nThat turned into the BN Restaurant Guide a 75-page companion that helps you enjoy meals like:\n🍕 A thin-crust, multigrain veggie pizza with olives & zucchini\n 🍛 Chicken Kolhapuri with phulkas instead of naan\n 🥤 Iced lime water over sugary sodas\n 🍲 Grilled paneer with green salad and mint chutney\n\n Whether you're at a café, buffet, or sushi bar the guide shows you exactly: \n → What to eat\n → Portion sizes that keep you full, not stuffed\n → Smart swaps that don’t feel like sacrifices\n → Tips to stay on track, even when dining out",
