    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "We’re always looking for the next big health trend, but I’ve found that some of the best superfoods are already in my kitchen.\n\nSome of my favourites are: \n1. Mint: Summer coolant & aids digestion. \n2. Coriander seeds (Dhaniya): Great detox & helps blood sugar regulation.\n3. Cinnamon: Curbs random cravings & supports metabolism.\n4. Turmeric: Fights inflammation & gives immunity a boost.\n5. Carom Seeds (Ajwain): A go-to for bloating & gut relief.\n\nAt Balance Nutrition, we make the most of these simple kitchen superfoods. Maintaining weight & health doesn’t have to be complicated, it really does start with what’s already in your spice box.\n\nWhich is your favourite Kitchen Superfood? Share it in the comments :)",
