    "descriptionPlain": "To know more about our online diet program and how we work, contact Krishna at +917021960648 \n\nDid you know that not everyone actually needs protein powders—and for some, they can even cause bloating?\n\nAt Balance Nutrition, we don’t believe in quick fixes, we believe in building health the smart way. Because when you add protein daily, you’re not just following a trend, you’re following science that supports energy, muscle repair & gut balance. ✅\n\nHere’s how to get protein right:\nFirstly, it depends from person to person-Many complain of bloating when they suddenly start powders\nStart by adding protein to every meal & let your gut adaptOnly then, consider protein powders—and that too after consulting a qualified nutritionist\n\nThese simple steps make sure your protein intake works with your body, not against it.\n\nWant to decode more smart nutrition hacks like this?\n\nComment “PROTEIN” below & we’ll DM you the details.\n\n(Protein Myths, Health Podcast, Smart Nutrition, Gut Friendly Eating, Protein For Women)\n\n#SmartNutrition #BalanceNutrition #MindfulEating #HealthyLifestyle #NutritionTips #KhyatiRupani #PodcastIndia",
