    "videoUrl": null,
    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Comment “inflammation' if you want to lose weight & reverse Inflammation without any exercise. \n\nDisha, based in Australia, was struggling with weight gain for years. Very skeptically, she decided to give the diet programs @bn a last chance. \n\nWhat did we do?\nHer diets were practical and sustainable. \nWe kept her meals simple, combining homemade favorites with occasional outside food. \n\nShe also cooked in bulk for herself and her husband, storing meals in the fridge to save time during the week.\n\nFast forward to today, and Disha has lost an incredible 32kg & her battle with severe inflammation is now over! \nHer journey is far from over, she’s set to lose 32 kg more & has new dress sizes to fit in :)",
    "tags": [],
