    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Wondering if ghee for fat loss really works? Can traditional Indian food reverse PCOS, thyroid issues, and heal your gut?\n\nIn this life-changing episode, Khyati Rupani (Founder, Balance Nutrition) shares her incredible 40kg transformation story, PCOS reversal food plan using desi ingredients, and how she built India's most trusted nutrition platform with 75,000+ clients across 94 countries.\n\nThis Khyati Rupani podcast busts the calorie counting myth India struggles with, reveals gut healing foods Indian kitchens already have, and gives you actionable desi eating tips for real, sustainable weight loss women can maintain for life.\n\nKey Takeaways:\n• Weight loss Indian diet tips without cutting out ghee and local food\n• The PCOS reversal food plan Indian women rely on\n• Why calorie counting fails for Indian meals and families\n• Gut healing foods Indian diets already provide\n• How to use ghee for fat loss backed by science, not fad\n• Gluten myths Indian food lovers should ignore\n• Thyroid diet plan India: what really works\n• Fat loss after 30 India: practical, lifestyle-driven help for women\n• How to fix hormonal belly fat with food, not supplements\n• Desi eating tips for work, events, flights, and busy days",
