    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Confused by all the nutrition noise online? You’re not alone! 🍽️\n\nIn this eye-opening episode, Celebrity Clinical Nutritionist Khyati Rupani, Founder of Balance Nutrition, joins Devendra Mohan (Devendra Talks) to uncover the real truths about diet, diabetes, PCOS, fatty liver, and Indian eating habits that no one’s talking about.\n\nWith 20+ years of experience and over 75,000 clients served, Khyati reveals:\n⚡ Why most diet plans fail (and how to make them work for you)\n🥜 The shocking truth about biscuits, peanut butter, and so-called “healthy snacks”\n💔 What’s really causing fatty liver and weight gain in Indian families\n🧃 The hidden dangers of processed foods, sugary drinks, and kids’ eating habits\n💪 How to manage diabetes, PCOS, and hormonal imbalance with simple desi nutrition principles\n\nWhether you want to lose weight, manage diabetes, or simply understand your body better, this episode breaks down science-backed Indian nutrition in the most relatable way possible.",
