    "videoUrl": null,
    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "In this eye-opening episode of Trending Diaries, Celebrity Nutritionist Khyati Rupani from Balance Nutrition uncovers the truth behind PCOS, Endometriosis, and Hormonal Imbalances, and explains how the right diet can completely transform women’s health. \n\nIf you’ve ever wondered why your diet isn’t helping your hormones or why PCOS without weight gain is still so common, this conversation is for you. Learn the science behind food, hormones, and inflammation, simplified for Indian women with busy lifestyles.\n\nYou’ll learn:\n🍽️ Why women with normal weight can still have PCOS, and how food directly influences hormones\n🔥 Anti-inflammatory diet tips for Endometriosis management and pain reduction\n🧠 The most common hormonal diet mistakes women make\n💪 How to plan a fertility-friendly diet for improved reproductive health\n⏰ Simple, sustainable eating routines for working women\n💡 How nutrition, stress, and inflammation are all connected\n\nNo fad diets. No quick fixes. Just real, science-backed nutrition strategies that help you feel better, stronger, and more balanced.",
