    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Why 95% Fail at Weight Loss: Khyati Rupani Reveals the Real Mistakes!\n\nJoin Celebrity Nutritionist Khyati Rupani (Founder, Balance Nutrition) and Fitness Coach Yash as they reveal real secrets to weight loss, PCOS reversal, and sustainable fitness for Indian men and women.\n\nThis power-packed conversation dives deep into Indian diet myths, hormonal balance, nutrition for workouts, and healthy eating habits that actually work in the long run. Whether you're struggling with cravings, fatigue, or plateaus in weight loss, this video gives you science-backed, practical solutions — not fads!\n\n💡 Learn how to:\n✅ Lose weight naturally without crash diets\n✅ Beat PCOS and balance hormones through food\n✅ Plan the perfect Indian meal plate\n✅ Manage nutrition for gym & home workouts\n✅ Eat right for your age, gender, and lifestyle\n✅ Make smart choices while eating out\n✅ Understand the difference between quick fixes vs sustainable health",
