    "descriptionPlain": "My Favourite Actor Ram Kapoor Loses 42kg in 7 Months at 51 Years of Age!\n\nHe is easily the Transformation of 2024!\n\nLet’s find out how he managed it:\nInstead of taking the easier way out and opting for Ozempic, Ram has diligently followed the 16-hour Intermittent Fasting method to achieve this transformation.\n\nHow to Lose Weight After Turning 40 & What Does It Entail?\n1. Forget Low-Calorie Diets: Focus on protein, complex carbs, and healthy fiber.\n2. Forget Shortcuts: No drug can help you lose weight without severely impacting your thyroid, liver, or kidneys.\n3. Forget Regular Late Nights: These affect your weight and health the most.\n4. Forget Diet Sodas and Regular Alcohol Intake: Alcohol is a neurotoxin and even more harmful to the body after 40.\n5. Intermittent Fasting Works— but only with guidance from a trained senior nutrition expert!\n\nDon’t miss our great year-end offers—ending soon!\n\n#RamKapoor #WeightLoss #Transformation #IntermittentFasting #Ozempic #Nutrition #BalanceNutrition #KhyatiRupani",
