    "descriptionPlain": "This is what Japanese women eat instead of chai samosa, and it might be why they have looked younger, leaner, and glowier for years!\n\nOn my Japan trip recently, I made real sushi by hand and discovered it's not just delicious… It’s a whole anti-aging, anti-bloat, anti-craving meal in one!\n\nCold sticky rice = digestion friendly, low insulin spikeShiso leaves, yuzu, radish = detox + antioxidant powerReal wasabi & seaweed = gut + metabolism supportNo dairy. No sugar. No junk. Still so satisfying. No post-meal bloat.\n\nSave this reel for a must-try experience on your next visit to Japan.\n\n➡️ If you found this video helpful, Subscribe for more and follow us on social media for daily wellness tips!\n  Khyati Rupani -   / nutritionist_khyatirupani  \n  Balance Nutrition -   / balancenutrition.in  \n  Facebook -   / balancenutrition.in  .\n\n#weightloss #fitness #fitnessmotivation #motivation #healthy #transformation #fitnessjourney #japan",
