    "videoUrl": null,
    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "To know more about our online diet program and how we work, contact at Barkha +919152419848 \n\nWhat I Eat at an Airport Lounge as a Nutritionist who lost 40kg twice and helped 75,000+ people lose weight!\n\nAirport lounges are a buffet paradise. The menu looks tempting, but here’s how I keep it balanced:\n\nHalf my plate filled with veggies & saladSmall portion of riceA cheat meal (yes, pasta counts!)A bowl of curd for protein & digestion\n\nThe trick? Smart plating over strict dieting.\nBecause when you plate mindfully, even airport lounges won’t derail your health goals.\n\nThis is exactly what I teach my clients too, how to enjoy meals anywhere without guilt, stress, or calorie counting. \n\nComment \"DIET\" if you also want to eat mindfully without stressing about calories, and I will be glad to help you.\n\n(Travel hacks, Healthy dining, Smart plating, Portion control, Balanced lifestyle, Food tracking, Personalised choices, Menu tracking, Calorie capping, Real-time feedback, Mindful eating, Lifestyle nutrition)\n\n#smartplating #mindfuleating #travelnutrition #airportlife #healthychoices #nutritionsimplified #balancenutrition",
