    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "What I eat at an Airport Lounge After Losing 40kg Twice & Helping 75,000+ People Transform!\n\nAirport lounges are a buffet paradise. The menu looks tempting, but here’s how I keep it balanced.\n\n1. Half the plate filled with veggies & salad\n2. A small portion of rice\n3. One cheat meal (yes, pasta counts!)\n4. A bowl of curd for protein & digestion\n\nThe trick? Smart plating over strict dieting.\nBecause when you plate mindfully, even airport lounges won’t derail your health goals.\n\nThis is exactly what we teach our clients to do, how to enjoy meals anywhere without guilt, stress, or calorie counting.\n\n👉 Comment “DIET” if you also want to eat mindfully without stressing about calories, and our team will be glad to help you.\n\nDo you count your Airport Capories?\n\n(Travel hacks, Healthy dining, Smart plating, Portion control, Balanced lifestyle, Food tracking, Personalised choices, Menu tracking, Calorie capping, Real-time feedback, Mindful eating, Lifestyle nutrition)",
    "tags": [
      "smartplating",
      "healthylifestyle",
      "healthyliving",
      "nutritiontips",
      "weightlossjourney",
      "diet"
    ],
