    "descriptionPlain": "Why Your Protein Isn’t Working for Fat Loss!\n\nInstagram is all about: “Eat more protein if you want to lose weight post 40.”\n\nSo, you religiously started adding protein powders, protein bars, and still…\n- No inch loss\n- No weight loss\n- Cravings still showing up\n\nIf you ask me, I have examined many women over the last few years & I can clearly state that it is not just about eating more protein, but about understanding your body, hormonal imbalances & identifying the root cause.\n\nIn most cases, a sudden intake of a high-protein diet & rigorous workouts worsens Inflammation, leading to weight gain, bloating & other digestive issues.\n\nWhat is the best way to reverse Inflammation & lose weight, then?\n\n1. Contrary to popular belief, weight loss-friendly foods like raw salads, raw fruits, beans & pulses will worsen inflammation. A diet that is high in cooked vegetables, well-cooked millets & probiotic-rich foods like curds will address both Inflammation & weight.\n\n2. Superfoods from the Indian Kitchen, like Jeera (cumin), Turmeric Powder, Pepper Powder & Fennel Seeds are known to help with Inflammation, especially when had with hot water.\n\n3. Instead of lifting, HIIT & Aggressive cardio, rest & recovery are shown to heal the body & help with weight loss.\n\n4. Sleep cycle management is the most underrated remedy for weight loss & inflammation.\n\nWant to know how to structure your meals for fat loss in your 40s?\n\nComment “BALANCE” below if you’re looking for an online diet plan.\n\n(Protein and fat loss, weight loss after 40, women’s health, hormonal balance, gut health, inflammation, anti-inflammatory foods, Indian superfoods, sleep & weight loss, sustainable fat loss)",
