    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "For many of us, being on a diet plan means that no outings & holidays can be a pain. So, we never go on a diet ever.\n\nIf this is you, then read the rest of the caption 😍\n\nAt BN, our clients can enjoy their meals at their favourite restaurants, they can also choose their drinks smartly & snack up during their diet program. Their results are better than ever!\n\nHow is this possible?\n\nThe clients at BN use:\n\n1. The BN Restaurant Guide\n2. The BN Alcohol Guide\n3. The BN Quick-Fillers Guide\n\nAlong with their diets, these guides help them stay on track & makes it a practical, sustainable way ahead.\n\nWhat do they Skip?\n-Calorie Counting\n-Weighing Food\n-Stressing about food at all times\n\nWhat do they Follow?\n- The BN Guides\n- BN Recipes\n- BN Diets\n- Portion Control\n- Ideal Plating\n- Vacations, weddings & Parties\n\nWould you like to know more about us?\n\n(Food tracking, Smart logging, Personalized choices, Menu tracking, Calorie capping, Real-time feedback, Mindful eating, Lifestyle nutrition, Portion control, Healthy dining)",
