    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Tried Diet & Exercise, still no fat loss?\n\nIt could be these reasons👇🏻\n⁣⁣⁣⁣\n1. You are eating less but still can’t lose weight - in fact, you might even be gaining. ⁣⁣⁣⁣\n⁣⁣⁣\n2. You’re consistently doing HIIT or intense cardio classes, and your belly fat doesn’t budge\n⁣⁣⁣⁣\n3. You have changed nothing in the way you eat or work out, yet suddenly you are gaining weight. ⁣⁣⁣⁣\n⁣⁣⁣⁣\nYour body is storing fat! It’s just science. ⁣⁣⁣⁣\n⁣⁣⁣⁣\nWe spend all this time trying to do the right thing- the things we have been taught to be true. But actually, many times those are the things that sabotage us. ⁣⁣⁣⁣\n⁣⁣⁣⁣\nWhat you need:⁣⁣⁣⁣\n⁣⁣⁣\n- an adequate amount of food in the right ratios to spike your metabolism⁣⁣⁣⁣\n⁣⁣⁣⁣\n- a break from any kind of workouts\n⁣⁣⁣⁣\n- address hormone health and, more importantly, work on reducing inflammation\n⁣⁣⁣⁣\nIf you are one of them, comment “ANTI” & we shall DM you the details of our Anti-Inflammatory Program.\n\n(fat loss plateau, stubborn belly fat, weight gain reasons, anti-inflammatory diet, hormone health, metabolism boost, weight loss after 40)",
