    "descriptionPlain": "Comment 'YES' if you are ready to lose 10kg before Diwali!\n\nPunjabi film star and TV celebrity Shehnaaz Gill underwent a massive transformation a while ago.\nShe credits a balanced diet and Turmeric Tea for her dramatic weight loss.\n\nAs a nutrition expert, I completely approve of this method of weight loss :)\n\nHere is her Turmeric Tea Recipe:\n\nIngredients:\nTurmeric root: 1 inch\n(use half a tsp of powder if root is not available)\nApple Cider Vinegar: 1 tbsp\n\nMethod:\nBoil two cups of water and add grated fresh turmeric to it.\nLet it simmer for 7-8 minutes until it changes colour & turns dark.\nPour it into a cup and let it cool slightly. Add apple cider vinegar.\n\nHow to consume:\nHave it on an empty stomach every morning.\n\nP.S. THIS WILL WORK ONLY IF FOLLOWED BY A BALANCED DIET.\n\nWould you like to lose 10kg before Diwali?\n\n(shehnaaz gill weight loss, turmeric tea weight loss, lose 10kg, apple cider vinegar benefits, celebrity weight loss secrets)",
