    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Want a TEA that burns fat while keeping you refreshed?\n\nHere’s a simple yet powerful Weight Loss Tea Recipe made with Indian kitchen superfoods 👇\n\nINGREDIENTS\n* Cinnamon powder - ½ tsp\n* Ginger (fresh) - ½ inch 🫚\n* Saunf (fennel seeds) - ½ tsp\n* Mint leaves - 4-5 🍃\n* Whole pepper - 3-4\n* Water - 1.5 cups\n* Tea Bag (green, black tea) - 1\n* Honey - Optional\n\nDIRECTIONS:\n\nStep 1:\nAdd ginger, saunf, mint leaves, and whole pepper to a pounder & make a paste.\n\nStep 2:\nAdd the water to a pan & bring it to a boil. Add this paste to it.\n\nStep 3:\nLet it simmer for 2 minutes, sit for 5 minutes to absorb the compounds from the spices & enjoy hot.\n\n🍃Cinnamon, mint leaves, and saunf help you boost your metabolism, help in better digestion, and keep you full for hours, which aids in weight loss.\n\nTo know the best time to have this tea for good results?\n\nComment “TIME” and we shall send you the revert on DM 👍\n\nWant to lose 10 kg before Diwali?\n\n[saunf, mint leaves, cinnamon, tea, rain, monsoon, weight loss, monsoon tea, magic tea, fat burning tea, weight loss tea, weight loss tea recipe]",
