    "descriptionPlain": "Think \"Cold-Pressed\" Means Fewer Calories? Think Again! 🛑\n\nMost people think some oils are \"healthier\" than others because they're cold-pressed or labeled as heart-friendly. But here’s the truth that Nutritionist Khyati Rupani decodes in our latest podcast: 🎉🤯✨\n\n🔥 All oils are 100% cholesterol-free (because only animal products contain cholesterol).\n🔥 Every oil has the SAME calories – whether it's olive, coconut, or vegetable oil.\n🔥 What matters most is the type of fat inside – some oils are packed with healthy fats, others… not so much!",
