    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Are you constantly feeling hungry? Oats Can Be Your Best Friend.\n\nOats are naturally processed, 100% no preservatives, no additives. They are uncomplicated, real food, that nourishes without any preservatives or extra, undesirable additives.\n\nBenefits of oats are:\n\n👉 High in soluble fibre\n\n👉 Good for weight loss\n\n👉High protein content than most grains\n\n👉 More antioxidants than broccoli\n\n👉 Controls blood sugar\n\n👉 Reduces bad cholesterol\n\nFeast freely on our wholesome recipe ✅",
