    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "There are many reasons why people are hesitant to start with a diet program! Watch this video series to know why.\n\nReason 3: Trying to understand the calorie count! \n\nBefore you start to eat a meal do you have to start counting calories?\n\n👉🏻 Calorie counting is a job of a Nutritionist and they surely have an expertise in it. So you don't have to worry about calories while eating every meal and make the weight loss journey tiring!\n\nWant to know how we tackle this here at Balance Nutrition?\n\nHere at BN we help our clients understand and learn the concept of portion size, food groups so that they can maintain their weight well!",
