    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Ever noticed how roti, rice, and dal just don’t feel the same anymore?\n\nGrowing up, these were the staples in our home.\nBut back then, roti was made from grains ground at home.\nRice wasn’t ready in 10 minutes. It took time, and it had all the fiber.\n\nNow?\nIt’s all refined.\nRoti feels like maida.\nRice is just starch.\nWe eat, we feel sleepy.\nAnd slowly, our health pays the price. Weight gain, fatigue, even fatty liver.\n\nThe truth is, our ancestors knew what they were doing.\nThey ate whole foods. They took time to cook.\nAnd they didn’t need diets, detoxes, or supplements.\n\nMaybe we don’t need to eat less.\nMaybe we just need to eat like they did.",
