    "descriptionPlain": "Adding 2 tsp of Raw mangoes or Kacchi Kairi to your lunch & dinner can have these benefits: 🥭 \n\n1. It helps the liver to secrete Bile, an enzyme responsible for breaking up the fat & aiding weight loss. ✅\n\n2. It contains an antioxidant Mangiferin, found only in raw mangoes. This antioxidant helps balance your blood cholesterol, triglycerides and fatty acids. ❤️\n\n3. It is extremely rich in vitamin C, a nutrient that is responsible for good skin and hair.✅\n\nThe best way to add it in your diet is this easy recipe that is shown in the video.❤️\n\nOil free pickle - suitable for Weight watchers, diabetics & heart patients.\n\nRaw Mango - 1 cup \nOnions - 1 cup \nTomatoes - 1 cup \n\nAdd lime, chilli powder & salt to taste.\n(Those having high blood pressure can avoid the salt, it tastes equally good 😊)\n\nI enjoy it with Dal & Brown rice the most ❤️\n\n(diet) (summer nutrition) (mango) (kacchi kairi) (hair health) ( skin care)",
