    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Fennel tea commonly known as sauf Ki chai helps with Bloating & PCOS.\n\nWhile we all know that fennel seeds help in digestion and are commonly used in India after a meal as digestive, very few people are aware of its benefits in managing hormonal imbalances!\n\nFennel seeds help in reducing androgen, a male hormone, in the body which can help decrease hirsutism (excessive hair on the face).\n\nRecipe:\n\n• Mix 2 tsp fennel seed powder in 1.5 cups of water & boil for 5 minutes on a slow flame.\n\n• Strain & have this with lime.\n\nIdeal time:\n\nBefore breakfast & after dinner 😇\n\nTo know more about our Beat PCOS Diet Program, contact us:\n\nCall/WhatsApp:\nNutritionist Chelsi: 9820455544\nNutritionist Akansha: 9820792855",
