    "descriptionPlain": "Fat Burning Tea Recipe:\n\nAlong with aiding weight loss, this Tea is anti-inflammatory & has immune-boosting properties. \n\nMETHOD:\nStep 1: Slow boil 1.5 cups of water.\nStep 2: Add the Turmeric powder to the water while it's boiling. \nStep 3: Boil for 1 min on a slow flame until it is reduced to 1 cup. \nStep 4: Add to a cup, add the black pepper powder & juice of a quarter of a lime.\n\nBEST TIME TO HAVE:\nHave this Early morning on an empty stomach for 2 weeks. Let us know how much weight you have lost once done :)\n\nREMINDER:\nThis drink will not work on its own without a healthy & sustainable diet & lifestyle plan.",
