    "descriptionPlain": "Hair Fall Prevention Drink Recipe! \n\nIdeal for those who have dry, brittle hair that is facing breakage. \n\nMake this drink using: \n\nStrawberries 🍓 \nBlueberries 🫐 \nCucumber 🥒 \nMint leaves 🍃 \nLemon 🍋 \nCold water 💦 \n\nInfuse the water overnight (if living in cold regions) or for 5 to 6 hours (if the weather is above 20 degrees).\n\nIdeal Time: \n\nHave it on an empty stomach or before breakfast to see the best results. \n\n(Refrigerate the bottle if you stay in a hot & humid city)\n\nP.S. You can eat the berries and cucumber afterward ;)",
