    "descriptionPlain": "Mango Mithai Recipe for Weight Watchers!\n\nIf you are on a path to losing weight, are having PCOS, or have high blood sugars but want to enjoy mangoes, here is how you can :)\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n- Oats - 15 g\n- Skim Milk / Nut Milk - 75 ml\n- Mangoes (chopped) - 1 no.\n- Nuts (roasted, crushed) - 3 nos.\n\nDIRECTIONS:\n- In a jar or bowl combine all ingredients together. \n- Cover the jar or bowl and place in the fridge overnight or for at least 4 hours. \n- Remove from fridge, and enjoy.\n\nP.S You can have 1 bowl of this thrice a week in breakfast or 2 katoris of this per week as dessert :)",
