    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Low-Calorie Thandai Recipe for Weight Watchers this Holi!\n\nA regular glass of Thandai can give you almost 400 calories & if you don’t stop at 1, you only end up guzzling the entire day’s calorie allowance by having only 4 glasses! \n\nHere is a recipe that reduces your calories by 300 per glass!\n\nINGREDIENTS:\nMilk (skim, nut, oat) - 1 glass\nHoney - 1 tsp (optional)\nDried Rose Petals - 1 tsp\nPistachios (Chopped)- 1 tsp\nYou can also add cardamon powder, fennel powder & even pepper powder to enhance the taste, no harm done :)\n\nMix all the ingredients in a shaker, add some ice cubes & give it a good shake. \n\nServe chilled topped with nuts & petals! \n\nP.S. Treat yourself to 2 glasses if you like it :)",
