    "descriptionPlain": "Add 15g protein that is natural, easy to digest & low in calories to your diet with this Drink. \n\nIt also has calcium, iron & probiotics. \n\nFind the recipe below: \n\nIngredients: \n*Sattu flour - 3 tbsp\n*Water / buttermilk made in Greek yogurt - 1 glass\n*Lime juice - 1/2 tsp\n*Mint leaves - 4 to 5 \n*Roasted cumin powder - 1/2 tsp\n*Black salt / Chaat masala - as needed \n\nHere's how you can make it: \n\nStep 1: Prepare sattu flour by grinding roasted horse gram to a fine powder. \n\nStep 2: Take a vessel, add sattu flour, water or buttermilk and mix well. \n\nAdd lemon juice, mint leaves, black salt, roasted cumin powder and mix well.\n\nStep 3: Pour into a glass, add ice cubes and serve.\n\nIdeal in summer for your entire family!",
