    "videoUrl": null,
    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Comment ‘YES’ if you’re ready to start your wellness program with us :)\n\nINGREDIENTS for 1 Serving Super Drink:\n\n4 tsp Sattu (roasted gram flour)\n2 tsp Gond Katira (pre-soaked)\nPinch of pink salt\n1 tsp Roasted Jeera Powder\n200 ml Buttermilk (chass)\n\n Method:\n➡️ In a glass, add satu, gond katira, pink salt, and roasted jeera powder.\n➡️ Pour in chilled buttermilk and stir until smooth.\n➡️ Top with fresh coriander leaves and enjoy!\n\nWhy I love it (and why you will too):\n\nSatu keeps you full and gives your body clean plant protein & it’s easy on digestion.\nGond katira is a natural body-cooler & aids weight loss. \nPink salt helps your body stay hydrated and balances your sodium.\nRoasted jeera powder does wonders for bloating and supports digestion.\nButtermilk is light, probiotic-rich, and great for your gut.\nCoriander adds freshness and a dose of vitamin C.\n\nWill you add this to your diet?",
