    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "☕ From 600 to 60 CALORIES!\n\nHere’s how I order my Starbucks coffee as a nutritionist 🍵👇\n\nA tall Frappuccino at Starbucks is loaded with sugar and cream, and if you add extra flavors, it’s packed with artificial ingredients too.\n\nAs a nutritionist who finds ways to enjoy most foods, I’ve figured out a smarter Starbucks coffee order as well! 😉\nI go for an Iced Americano (0 calories) and ask for 30ml of Vanilla Sweet Cream (60 calories).\n\nIn India, we don’t yet have the sugar-free, 0-calorie Vanilla Sweet Cream, but if you’re traveling abroad, do ask for it.\n\nThis option is safe for those looking to lose weight, people with controlled diabetes, as well as those managing uric acid and thyroid issues.\n\nWill you try this Summer Coffee hack ?",
