    "descriptionPlain": "Comment “Ideal Time” to know the best time to have it.\n\nThis iced tea isn’t just a summer cooler—it’s basically a glow potion in disguise ✨🍃\n\nAs a nutritionist, I always say: glowing skin and healthy hair don’t start with what you put on your skin, but with what you put in your body. And this little drink? It’s one of my absolute favorite skin glow rituals, especially when the weather heats up.\n\nI call it my *Skin Glow Iced Tea* 🌿\n\nIt’s super simple and so effective: I use the Tulsi Moringa Herbal Mix from @Satopradhan.store (it’s clean, potent, and packed with antioxidants), add a squeeze of fresh lime, a spoon of soaked chia seeds, and pour it all over ice. That’s it!\n\n💚 It helps reduce inflammation\n💚 Supports collagen production\n💚 Clears up the skin and boosts hair health\n💚 Aids in weight balance\n💚 And it’s super hydrating and delicious\n\nJust mix half a teaspoon of the herbal tea in warm water, stir in the lime and chia, pour it over ice—and enjoy! It’s honestly my go-to for a refreshing glow boost from the inside out.\n\nBecause real beauty starts within... and yes, it can taste this good 🌞\n.",
