    "descriptionPlain": "Cleanse your Kidney & Liver with this drink ✅\n\nCoriander and cardamom tea:\n🌿 Reduces water retention \n🌿 Lowers blood sugar \n🌿 Lowers blood pressure \n🌿 Helps with kidney detox \n🌿 Helps fight acidity\n\nWhen to drink?\n\nHave 1 cup before bed for best results\n\nHow to prepare?\n\nRequired ingredients: \n* Cardamom pieces - 4-5 no. \n* Coriander leaves - ½ Katori \n* Water - 1 cup\n\nDirections:\nHeat the water in a vessel or a teapot until it boils. Roughly chop the coriander leaves and add them to the boiling water. Add the cardamom pieces to the water as well. Let it cold until it reaches a lukewarm temperature so that the coriander leaves can infuse in properly. Filter the mixture and your tea is ready to be consumed.",
