    "descriptionPlain": "A lot of us are suffering from gastrointestinal disorders. \n\nThe common symptoms of this seasonal illness are loose motion, vomiting & diarrhoea.\n\n The immediate danger to our health is that of dehydration. Since the appetite is low, an ORS (Oral rehydration solution) is the 1st line of treatment.\n\nAn oral rehydration solution is used to treat moderate dehydration. \n\nIt’s made of water, glucose, sodium, and potassium. \n\nBENEFITS: \nThe combination optimizes the absorption of fluid in the intestines, which helps quickly replenish fluids. \n\nDo like & share!",
