    "descriptionPlain": "Low Hemoglobin Remedy from Khyati’s Kitchen ✅\n\nThis juice is best to have on an empty stomach daily. \n\nRECIPE:\n- 2 Beetroot & Carrot (peeled) \n- 2 Amlas\n- 1 inch piece of Ginger (Adrak)\n- 1/2 Bunch of Spinach (Palak) \n- 1 Lime (squeeze the juice) \nBlend these ingredients properly in a juicer until puréed. Strain if too thick. Squeeze lime juice to this. Also, you can additionally add a pinch of cinnamon powder to this.\n\nThe anti-oxidants & vitamins in this juice will help you cleanse your liver & supply your body with a lot of vitamins! \n\nThe addition of lime juice makes the iron from the vegetables easily available for absorption\n\nP.S.  Do not throw the residue, use those veggies to make a tikki, chilla or just take it & apply it to your face :)",
