    "descriptionPlain": "Think mangoes make you fat? Think again. \n\nSummer is the King Fruit’s season, just like this IPL was King Kohli’s season and as a nation, we all love mangoes as much as we love RCB!\n\nYet most of us have recently been avoiding mangoes, thinking they are unhealthy, full of sugar, making us fat & acne, which could not be further from the truth\n\nFacts👇\n\n-> Beta Carotene & antioxidants = stronger immunity\n-> Vitamin C = glowing skin & healthy hair\n-> Packed with magnesium, potassium & sodium = a happy heart\n\nTips👇\n\n* Always soak your mangoes before eating\n* Eat your mangoes, don’t drink them\n* Eat between meals (between breakfast & lunch or lunch & dinner)\n\nComment ‘MANGO’ if you want to start your fat-loss journey with us without giving up your favourite fruits!\n\n(Sugar, Calories, Wellness, Weight Loss, Natural Sugar, Myth Busting, Sweeteners, Fitness, Lifestyle Nutrition, Mango, Healthy Eating, Nutrition)",
