    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Bloating, Fatigue, Dull Skin? It all starts with your gut.\n\nAs a nutritionist, I see this all the time clients coming in with bloating, fatigue, or low energy.\n\nProblem?\nUnhappy gut.\n\nSo, this is an Indian gut-friendly meal plan:\n\n- Ragi & oats - full of fibre, easy on the gut.\n- Curd & kadhi - our desi fermentation.\n- Papaya, beetroot, dudhi - hydrating, light, and soothing\n- Elaichi, warm water, green tea - best for post-meals.\n\nNo exotic superfoods. \nNo complicated routines. \n\nOnly simple choices that help your gut (and you) feel a little more balanced.\n\n(Khyati Rupani, Balance Nutrition, Diet Plan, Constipation, Bloating, Acidity)",
