    "descriptionPlain": "The hardest word for the human brain to comprehend is “NO.”\n\nSo when you’re on a diet that excludes a lot of foods, you’re bound to fail at some point.\n\nAt Balance Nutrition, all our clients swear by the BN Restaurant Guide, which helps them socialise and eat out smartly while staying on track with their program.\n\nCraving Chinese? Ordering in? Eating out? Follow these simple tips:\n\n💧 Choose sparkling water instead of sugar-loaded drinks.\n🥬 Go for veggies that are sautéed, not soaked in oil.\n🥡 Make your rice or noodles 50% veggies (yes, that’s allowed!).\n🥵 Order chilli paneer, but ask them to skip the frying.\n\nYou’ll be happy to know this smart ordering can cut your meal’s calories by half, leading to minimal deviation in your weight loss journey!\n\nWant to know more about our online diet programs or the BN Restaurant Guide?\nComment “Chinese” below, and we’ll DM you the details! 😊\n.\n.",
