    "id": "812",
    "title": "Heatwave (loose motion, random acidity, bloat)",
    "category": "PCOS",
    "subType": "Gyan",
    "mediaType": "static",
    "videoUrl": null,
    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "If your stomach’s throwing a full-on summer tantrum… don’t worry, it’s probably not just you being dramatic, blame the heat! 😵‍💫🔥\n\nLoose motions? Random acidity? That mysterious afternoon bloat?\n\nNope, it’s not Mercury retrograde. It’s that sketchy leftover you thought was still good. 👀\n☀ In this kinda heat, food turns faster than your mood on a Monday morning.\n\nThat paneer tikka sitting out “just for a bit”? Yeah... it’s plotting against you.\n\nAnd when your gut’s upset, your vibes follow. Every. Single. Time.\n\n✨ So, what can you actually do?\n\n🧊 Refrigerate like you mean it, don’t just shove stuff in the fridge, make sure it’s cool enough to keep it fresh.\n\n🥣 Stick to fresh food if it smells “kind of okay,” it’s probably not.\n\n💧 Chaas + a pinch of pink salt = summer lifesaver, hello hydration and happy gut!\n\n🧠 Eat right, feel right, your nutrition is working overtime behind the scenes, so show it some love.\n\nBasically, your gut is texting you in all caps. Time to listen and give it the summer TLC it deserves. 😮‍💨\n\n#HotGirlSummer but for your gut ✨",
