    "descriptionPlain": "Watching reels at bedtime can have a lot of side effects.\n\nEn listing a few of them that are related to your overall health and weight. \n\n1. it disrupts your sleep cycle leading to incomplete rest, which has a lot of physical as well as psychological health hazards.\n2. ⁠ Most of you will also want to munch on something while doing so, meaning that you will end up adding more calories late at night.\n3. ⁠ This also eats into a lot of our productive time for the next day which is spent battling less sleep.\n\nThis also impacts your hormonal balance which leads to a lot of weight gain. \n\nSo, if you want to continue watching reels, ensure that it is only for a stipulated period of time during the day. \n\nYou will be surprised at the amount of free hours you have during your day to accomplish things like cooking, healthy and exercising.",
