    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "While losing weight & reversing Thyroid, Our client Shruti realised that it was never about weighing food, counting calories, managing meals on time or eliminating foods.\n\nWhat helped her the most to get rid of body fat & Thyroid was realising these 3 mistakes she was making with her food. \n\nMISTAKE 1: \n\nCounting Calories: \n\nShe was getting frustrated & started hating dieting overall.\nShe also went off track many times & cheated. \n\nMore than calories, it is important to understand “portion size”.\n\nMISTAKE 2:\n\nNot estimating liquid calories:\n\nYou can add 2000 cal in your daily diet by consuming a milkshake, cold drinks, frappes & fruit juice.\n\nMISTAKE 3: \n\nConfusing thirst with hunger:\n\nMany of us don’t realise that the body is thirsty, not hungry. This is because of ignoring the thirst signal, it gets impaired. Leads to excessive consumption of food. \n\nIf you are hungry, have water first, then go for food.\n\nAlong with this, she was on a healthy diet & her mentor was always available to solve her doubts!\n\n(Weight loss) (Thyroid reversal) (Healthy diet) (Portion control) (Liquid calories) (Nutrition mentor) (Healthy habits) (Calorie counting mistakes) (Diet mistakes)",
