    "descriptionPlain": "INTERMITTENT FASTING - IS IT THE BEST?\n\nFor most of you, intermittent fasting is all about ensuring that you are fasting for a long period of time. The whole stress is given to the fasting hours. \n\nWhile there is a lot of substantial evidence about the benefits of fasting, it only works if you’re eating window is appropriately managed with proper eating pattern and diet. You cannot call it intermittent fasting if you’re eating window comprises of all the junk and wrong foods. \n\nIn short, intermittent fasting does not work with Only fasting hours. \nIt works with a balance of fasting and a good diet plan during the eating window. \n\nTo know more, DM us :)",
