    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "3 Non-Diet Hacks or Tips That Helped Me Lose Stubborn Body Fat After 40 are as follows:\n\n💥 After losing 40 kg 15 years ago and transforming my life, I realized I was gaining body fat after turning 40 last year. \nI realized my old dietary habits had nothing to do with this gain & there were other factors that I needed to work on.\n\n1️⃣ Tracking my emotions & staying calm 🧘‍♀️ \nStress plays a huge role in weight gain, especially due to cortisol spikes. I began tracking my emotions daily, learning not to react aggressively and focusing on calmness. It helped me break the stress-fat cycle. \n\n2️⃣ No starvation, no alcohol 🚫 \nExtreme dieting? Not for me. I limited alcohol to 1 glass a fortnight and stopped starving myself unknowingly when at work. My metabolism thanked me for it. \nNourishing my body with the right foods kept my energy up and helped me lose extra fat sustainably.\n\n3️⃣ Weight training (even when I hated it!) 🏋️‍♀️ \nI’ll admit, I wasn’t a fan of weight training, but doing it just twice a week has been a game changer. It boosted my metabolism, strengthened my muscles, and helped me burn more fat.",
