    "videoUrl": null,
    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Just because your parents have diabetes doesn’t mean you will! \n\n Here’s the REAL reason you might get it…👇”\n\nGenetics alone does NOT cause diabetes—it’s your lifestyle choices that trigger it. \n\n❌ Frequent blood sugar spikes – Too much sugar & refined carbs lead to insulin resistance.\n❌ Being sedentary – Lack of movement reduces your body’s ability to regulate blood sugar.\n❌ Chronic stress & poor sleep – High cortisol messes with insulin function.\n❌ Belly fat accumulation – Visceral fat is directly linked to metabolic disorders.\n❌ Nutrient deficiencies – Low fiber, magnesium & omega-3 levels worsen insulin resistance.\n\nTag a friend who needs to know this in the comments & spread awareness.\n\n(Diabetes, Hereditary, Lifestyle, Nutrition, Healthy Diet)",
