    "descriptionPlain": "YOU DON’T WANNA MISS THIS👇\n\nBut first, LIKE and FOLLOW for more daily fitness tips like this!\n\nThe Truth About ‘Sugar-Free’ Products! \n\nIn my recent podcast with Meri Saheli, we busted one of the biggest myths about sugar-free products. Many people assume sugar-free means healthy, but that’s far from the truth!\n\n🔸 Most sugar-free alternatives have more fat and calories than regular products.\n🔸 For diabetics, the real problem isn’t just sugar—it’s the entire processed package.\n🔸 The “sugar-free” label tricks us into eating more. Instead of one regular biscuit, you might eat four sugar-free ones!\n🔸 Sugar-free sweets made with figs and dates still spike blood sugar—just because they don’t contain white sugar doesn’t mean they’re safe.\n\n💡 DM us to get the link for the entire podcast.\n\nAre you a Diabetic?",
