    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "🚨 NEW EPISODE ALERT with @nutritionist_khyatirupani from @balancenutrition.in 🚨\n\nWe’re diving deep into ramadan tips, weight loss struggles, diet myths, and the real reason women find it harder to lose weight! 💡🔥\n\nFrom breaking the binge-restrict cycle to hormones ruining your progress, this episode is packed with eye-opening insights and practical tips (especially for Ramadan & women’s health!).\n\n📿Ramadan and diet mistakes \n💬 Why do we regain weight after losing it?\n🥗 The biggest diet lies we still believe!\n⏳ Fasting for weight loss – are you doing it wrong?\n🧠 How mindset is the REAL key to fat loss!\n🚺 Women vs. Men – Why does weight loss feel unfair?\n\nIf you’ve struggled with weight loss, this episode is a must-watch! 🎙️✨\n\n📺 Watch the full podcast now on YouTube! 🎧 Available on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Amazon Music & more\n.",
