    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Meet Khyati Rupani, a powerhouse of motivation, wisdom, and realness! 💥\n\nShe’s not just a renowned nutritionist, she’s someone who has lived the journey, losing 40kgs twice, working with 75,000+ clients, and proving that weight loss isn’t about restrictions, it’s about balance and mindset.\n\nWhat makes Khyati different? Her peppy, no-BS approach! She doesn’t believe in guilt-tripping, extreme diets, or impossible meal plans. Instead, she helps people, especially women, understand how food and lifestyle actually works in real life.\nHer energy is infectious, her advice is relatable, and she has a way of making even the hardest health journeys feel possible. \n\nIf you’ve struggled with food, weight loss, or just staying consistent, Khyati is the person you need to hear from.\n\nWatch the full episode on Youtube, Spotify, Apple Podcast, Amazon Music, JioSaavn. Link in the bio! 🎧✨\n.",
