    "descriptionPlain": "4 tips to follow a healthy diet for busy women! 😍✨\n\n1. Refrigeration - Prep your meals in advance one evening a week & refrigerate them in individual portions. \n2. Pre-soak Pulses - You can make chana masala, hummus & a protein salad anytime!\n3. Ditch the Clock - Don't try to be super perfect with meal timings, change your ingredients first. \n4. Don't go Calorie Counting - You will get frustrated, follow the portion & ideal plating methods. \n\nThese are a sure way to stick to your diet without being stressed :) 🥗🍕\n\nAt Balance Nutrition, we always make it simpler, easier & smarter! ✨💫\n\nWant to know more about Balance Nutrition Diet plans? Let us know in the Poll! 🌟🎉",
