    "descriptionPlain": "Could you have inflammation?\n\nThen you’ll want to read this.\n\nAfter nearly seven months of research, my R&D team and I are thrilled to introduce ADVANCED versions of two of our most successful online diet programs.\n\nThis journey began when I turned 40 last year and suddenly noticed changes in my mood, bloating, periods, and even body fat.\n\nWith my adenomyosis (a type of endometriosis), things only got worse. That’s when my team and I at Balance Nutrition decided to deep dive into the impact of inflammation—especially in women and men over 30.\n\nWe studied how gluten, dairy, stress, and packaged foods affect overall well-being, especially for those experiencing inflammation due to an underlying health issue.\n\nAlthough my diet programs have always been naturally anti-inflammatory, we have now developed ‘Intermittent Fasting Advanced’ & ‘Plateau Breaker Advanced’—specifically designed to address the root cause of inflammation.\n\nKey Features\n✔ Anti-inflammatory diets to target inflammation\n✔ Available only in 90-day & 180-day formats\n✔ A focused approach to reducing inflammation\n✔ Incorporates anti-inflammatory foods you already have in your kitchen\n✔ Includes gluten-free, lactose-free, and vegan meal ideas based on your needs\n\n🔗 Check out the program now: https://www.balancenutrition.in/advance-reform-intermittent",
