    "descriptionPlain": "Happy Sankranti to all our followers:)\n\nToday’s One Minute Wonder is all about Chikkis!\n\nWe must remember that Chikki, whether made with jaggery or sugar, is packed with high sugar and fat content.\n A serving can easily add up to 300 to 450 calories—that’s equivalent to a full Indian thali with roti, sabzi, dal, chawal, and salad! \nSo if you’re aiming to lose weight or manage your health, especially if you’re diabetic, be mindful of how much you consume.\n\n💡 TIP: If you can’t resist, just go for the Shagun-size portion - TWO bites.",
