    "descriptionPlain": "Being a dietitian isn’t just about cutting carbs or sugar. It’s about science, clinical training, and real experience.\n\nWhile quick-fix courses promise certifications in weeks, becoming a qualified nutritionist in India takes years of education, internships, and hands-on training.\n\n🎓 B.Sc in Nutrition & Dietetics\n🩺 Clinical internships\n📚 Postgraduate specialization\n🔬 Deep knowledge in anatomy, biochemistry, psychology, and more\n\nIn a world full of wellness trends and misinformation, credentials aren’t optional, they’re essential.\n\n- Backed by science\n- Tailored to your needs\n- Focused on long-term health\n\nTrust education. Trust experience. Trust the difference.",
