    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Craving restaurant food but not the side of guilt? 🍕\nFrom Chicken Tikka Masala to Chicken Enchiladas we’ve decoded the menus so you can enjoy your favorites without falling off track.\n\nAs part of our program, you’ll get access to our exclusive 75-page Restaurant Guide your go-to for smarter dining choices.\n✅ Portion tips\n✅ Healthier swaps\n✅ Multiple cuisines including Chinese favorites!\n\nTake a peek into our Chinese section\nInstead of defaulting to heavy noodles, try:\nVeg momos or sautéed baby corn & mushrooms as a light starter\nStir-fried veggies with your sauce of choice (skip the peanut!)\nMushroom or burnt garlic fried rice full of flavor, easy to portion\nNo guesswork. No guilt. Just confident, satisfying choices every time you eat out.\n\nComment “RESTAURANT” and we’ll DM you the podcast link with all the juicy details!\n\n(Weight Loss Goals, BN Restaurant Guide, Food Journaling, Balance Nutrition Community, Sustainable Health Tips)",
