    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "The most common reason for WEIGHT GAIN among Indians!\n\nMost of us do not recognize the THIRST signal. Hence, they often eat when they are actually thirsty.\n\nHow to train your brain to respond to the THIRST Signal\n\n1. First, drink a glass of water and wait ten minutes before eating again.\n2. After 10 minutes, if you’re still hungry, have a cup of black coffee without sugar.\n3. Wait for another 10 minutes. If you’re still hungry then It’s time to have a healthy snack.\n\nThis simple technique of listening to your body’s messages can make a big difference. Not only will it help you differentiate between thirst and hunger, but it will also help you lose weight by keeping you from the extra food you eat.\n\nWill you follow this hack?\n\n(weight loss, hungry, drink water, healthy lifestyle)",
