    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Disease v/s Disorder - 2 Very different conditions, know the difference!🤓❤️\n\nVery few understand the difference between the two, spending innumerable resources in treating disorder like a disease instead of mitigating the associated patterns of disorders. \n\nIn my latest podcast, Celebrity nutritionist @nutritionist_khyatirupani , founder of @balancenutrition.in explains the difference between the two! \n♥️\n\n- Disease when identified can be cured by Medical interventions, lifestyle changes, Mental outlook towards the disease. \nFor ex- Obesity & Stress induced metabolic syndromes can be cured. \n\n- Disorder which is usually a genetic disposition will remain regardless of the medical intervention but can be very well managed by lifestyle changes and adapting to an environment which is devoid of triggers. \nFor ex - PCOS, Thyroid, Diabetes are going to stay with you but you can very well change your lifestyle to co-exist with it but manage it. \n\nListen to the full 52Mins Masterclass to learn about Nutrition, Disease, Disorder, Managing conditions, losing weight and changing lives of thousands of people from around the world 💪🤓\n\nLink in bio❤️❤️❤️",
