    "descriptionPlain": "Hing ko English mai kya kehte hai?\nPata nahi & no worries also :)\n\nAlso known as asafoetida, Hing is commonly used in Indian khana.\n\nHere’s how you can consume it for better health & weight loss:\n\nIn a glass of warm water, add a pinch of Hing & have it 20 minutes before your meals. You can follow this mainly pre-dinner.\n\nThis will ensure you can digest your meals better and get rid of gas. And the most potent benefit?\n\nIt helps fight small infections in the gut.\n\n(Ig, reel, explore, trending, hing, cooking, food)\nWill you try this remedy?",
