    "descriptionPlain": "Kaju Katri vs. Shrikhand – Which Dessert is Better for Your Waistline this Diwali?\n\nLet’s break down the facts!\n\n🍥 Calories: Shrikhand comes in lighter than kaju katri, making it a smarter choice for all of us this festive season.\n\n🍥 Sugar & Fat Content: Shrikhand has less sugar & is lower in fat. Since it is made with curds, so we can feel good about the little protein & probiotics coming in ✅\n\nWhy Choose Shrikhand?\n\n💡 Ideal Portion: Limit to 50g serving with your meals to ensure minimal caloric disruption.\n\nDo you prefer Shrikhand or Kaju Katri?\n\nTell us in Comments!\n\n(Diwali Desserts, Healthy Choices, Festive Eating, Waistline Friendly, Shrikhand Benefits )",
