    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "“Hello to our Instagram family! 👋\n\nAfter helping me with gray and frizzy hair… I have one more concern that I need help with from you all ❗️\n\nEvery time I wear lenses, my eyes dry up and my vision starts to get foggy.. what to do when I don’t feel like wearing chasma?\n\nI’m in need of your opinion:\n\n- Should I go for a laser so no specs no lenses headache? Has any one of you got laser?\n\nOR\n\n- Get prescription sunglasses instead and wear specs rest of the day?\n\nAsking all of you wonderful people out there for advice!\n\nPlease offer your ideas and advice so that I can resolve my eye problem.\nYour opinions are much appreciated! 💡\n\nAdd your suggestions in comments for me :)\n\n(need your advice) (dry eyes) (summer) (lenses) (prescription-free sunglasses) (recommendation)",
