    "videoUrl": null,
    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "While losing 40 kg, I realised that it was never about weighing your food, counting your calories, managing your meals on time or eliminating foods.\n\nWhat helped me the most was this 1 hack.\n\nIt is also backed by a lot of scientific research, and there is also evidence that you can lose weight, especially body fat with this particular change in your day to day diet.\n\nThe star of the show here is FLaxseed & Cinnamon Tea!💫\n\nWith the help of this revitalizing Flaxseed and Cinnamon tea, transform your health! 🌿 ✨\n\nBenefits -\nFlaxseeds: - High in fiber, which facilitates fullness and aids in digestion, hence preventing overeating. - Has omega-3 fatty acids, which may help decrease cholesterol and are good for the heart. -\n\nCinnamon: - Lowers cravings for sweet meals by assisting in blood sugar regulation. - Has antioxidants, which may lessen inflammation and minimize the chance of developing chronic illnesses.\n\nLime: Packed with vitamin C, this fruit supports healthy skin and strengthens the immune system. - Enhances flavor without raising calorie or sugar content.\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n👉 Flaxseeds [whole or ground] - 2 tsp\n👉 Cinnamon powder - ¼ tsp\n👉 Lemon juice - ½ tsp\n👉 Water [boiling water] - 1 cup\n\n👩‍🍳 How to Prepare: -\n- For ten to fifteen minutes, add two teaspoons of whole or powdered flaxseed to one cup of hot water.\n- After straining the hot liquid, stir in ½ teaspoon each of lemon juice and cinnamon powder.\nP.S : To get results, Along with this tea, you must also follow a low fat healthy diet\n\n(Balance Nutrition) (Khyati Rupani) (Health tips of the day) (Healthy tea) (Herbal tea)",
