    "descriptionPlain": "How to lose weight without going on a diet!\n\nAs a nutritionist who lost 40kg & has maintained for 14 years, it was not possible to be on a diet at all times.\n\nThese 3 tips helped me manage my diet well & not go hungry or starve.\n\n1) Have foods that are high in volume and low in calories.\n2) Drink a glass of water 15 min before each meal.\n3) Add a serving of protein to all meals.\n\n(Nutrition) (Portion) (Low-fat) (low calorie food) (calorie consumption) (weight loss)",
