    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Glow Challenge: Tip 12 is Out!*\n\nAre you consuming the Alcohol in the right way?\n\nWhile most of us do they mix their alcohol with the energy drinks for better taste, but what we do not realize is that these energy drinks are not the right choice for mixing with alcohol, which leads to health issues.\n\nThe key to Drinking is always:\n\n✅ Drink in portion and only once a week\n\n✅ Always have your drink with plain soda or water\n\n✅ Have grilled paneer, grilled chicken salad or chickpeas\n\n❌ Avoid chips peanuts or any fried snacks\n\nP.S. – The safest amount of alcohol is always ‘No Amount’.\n\n(alcohol) ( consuming in the right way) ( right choice) (health) (energy drink) (what do not mix in alcohol)",
