    "descriptionPlain": "The first fear of going on a diet for every Indian is that he will have to give up on his morning and evening cup of chai 😓\n\nIt is never about the Tea that we worry about,but only about the extra additions to it. \n\nBiscuits, spoonfuls of sugar, chivdas, Samosa, sandwiches add extra calories & are generally high in fat as well.\n\nHence, your cup of tea is safe - Just not the other additions :)\n\nTip: Enjoy your masala tea, adrak tea, or Elaichi tea guilt-free with khakhra, Makhana, multigrain lavash, roasted kurmura & more!\n\nIn fact the masala tea loaded with spices is going to boost your immunity levels that will help you fight back infections!",
