    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Best way to lose fat!\n\nSpot reduction, Pills, powders, special formulas, garcinia, meal replacements, shakes, meal packets.\n\nNONE OF these are essential even in weight loss.\n\nIt's only smart & minor changes in the food leading to eating less calories from junk & sugar consumption that make weight loss happen.\n\nNo rocket science 🙂\n\nWe follow the same principles BalanceNutrition.in \n\n👉NO PILLS\n👉NO POWDERS\n👉NO STARVATION DIETS\n👉ONLY DELICIOUS & HEALTHY DIET PLANS",
