    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Have you been told this too???\n\nThere is NO evidence that dairy sabotages weight loss.\n\nIn fact calcium deficiency that comes along when you don’t consume dairy products will cause increase fat mass & less control over your appetite!\n\nThere are multiple factors that play a role in weight loss.\nSo before you quit dairy just for weight loss, RETHINK!\nMake sure you consult a nutritionist before to get alternatives included in your diet!",
