    "descriptionPlain": "Slim-N-Glow Challenge: Tip 4 is out!\n\nThis Tip is about “Beating your Sugar Cravings”. \n\nWhile most of us think they are healthy, they are high in natural sugar and calories. \nAlso, most times, they have calories similar to a small chocolate. \n\nSo instead of having dates here’s an alternative that has helped me & all our clients too. \n\n1. Take one liter of water (cold is good). \n2. Add fresh celery/mint leaves/coriander leaves \n3. Add the juice of half a lime\n\nSip this water or have a glass whenever you get the craving. It will disappear :)\n\nChew the leaves to get additional fiber & minerals. Aids in fat loss!\n\nThis hydrating drink not only satisfies your sweet cravings but supports your health goals and also helps in fat loss and staying hydrated.\n\nP.S. I have 2 bottles of this daily in summer. \n\n(healthy) (mom) (community) (engagement) (health goals) (wellness) (nutrition) (healthy goal) (low calorie) (celery) (good health)",
