    "descriptionPlain": "Slim-N-Glow Challenge: Tip 3 is out!\n\nFrom tomorrow, until the next 7 days, you will ensure walking at least 7000 steps daily. \nIf you already are, then try getting 8000, 9000 or 10,000 each day before dinner.\n\nWHAT IF YOU ARE NOT ABLE TO GET 7000 STEPS A DAY?\n\nThen your Dinner will be a bowl of fresh fruit + yogurt. \n\nHere are just a few reasons why hitting that 7000-step goal can make a big difference:\n1. Improved Cardiovascular Health\n2. Weight Management\n3. Increased Energy Levels\n4. Enhanced Mental Clarity \n\nWalking is a simple yet effective form of exercise that offers numerous health benefits, including improved cardiovascular health and increased calorie burn\n\nPro tip:\nMix Up Your Pace : Alternate between periods of brisk walking and slower, more leisurely strolls. This variation can help boost calorie burn.\n \n(weights loss) (steps goal) (calories burn) (healthy lifestyle) (eat healthy) (balance nutrition) (good food good mood)",
