    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Want to know how to sleep better? \n\nLook no further than the following tips that will help ensure that you actually have a good night! These tips inevitably come along with many more health benefits.\n\n1. Take the stairs: It enhances heart and lung function and improves blood circulation.\n\n2. Shop for groceries & daily essentials offline: One of the most effective ways to reduce belly fat is to regularly take part in aerobic exercise, such as walking.\n\n3. Be active throughout the day: Walking throughout the day greatly increases cardiovascular fitness, strengthens bones, reduces excess body fat, and boosts muscle power and endurance.\n\n4. Spend an entire day doing some mentally taxing but happy task: Staying mentally active plays a critical role in improving your sleep quality. People who lead intellectually stimulating lives are more likely to be free of dementia conditions like Alzheimer's disease.\n\nWould you like Khyati to make more videos like these?\nDo comment YES & we shall get going :)",
