    "videoType": null,
    "youtubeId": null,
    "imageUrl": null,
    "descriptionPlain": "Palak Paneer: Good to taste, but ZERO in Nutrition!!\n\nYes, that’s true. This is because ‘Palak’ is a source of iron and ‘Paneer’ is a source of calcium.\n\nWhen we consume Palak & Paneer together, the absorption of iron in Palak by our body is blocked by calcium in the paneer.\n\nThus depriving the body of iron which is a very essential mineral that forms blood.\n\nStill, craving for palak paneer????",
