    "descriptionPlain": "Most of us enjoy a glass of wine or a cocktail during weekends. \n\nWhile losing weight post-delivery with PCOS as a complication, I was keen on a glass of wine with friends during the weekend. \n\nSo, I decided to devise a guide that has a list of the most common alcoholic beverages, safe amounts, frequency of adding them to the diet & also a food guide.\n\nThis guide is called the BN Alcohol guide & has drinks, amounts & what foods to have while drinking & after.\n\nThe key to drinking is always:\n- Drink Smartly, stick to small & not large\n\n- Drink in Portion & only once a week \n\n- Accompany your Protein when drinking like hummus, chickpea salad, grilled paneer, or grilled chicken\n\n- Drink water before & after you consume alcohol. For every drink, have 2 glasses of water (1 before & 1 after) \n\n- Avoid chips, peanuts, or any fried snacks with your drink. \n\nTo know more about the Balance Nutrition Programs & the BN guides, you can connect with us on 9152419847",
