    "descriptionPlain": "Let's clear it.\nFear or Scared of CARBS?\nCarbs are highly controversial in the modern diets.\nNot getting enough carbs can be bad. Eating too many carbs is bad. What does a person do???‍?\nKhyati Rupani says,\nMany people reduce carbohydrate intake to help them lose weight, which shouldn't be a concern at all!!!!\nCarbohydrates are the most efficient fuel for the brain, the internal functions of the body as well as a very healthy source for energy.\nWestern diets swear by high protein as they always are meat eaters. High fat in the meats have harmful effects on cardiac health.\nOn the other hand, diets rich in fiber and complex carbs always prove to be safer, healthier and have high satiety making one feel full for long.\nSo avoid simple sugars, potatoes, pressure cooked white rice, refined flour, sago in case you want to lose weight and stick to oats, millets instead.\nThe right carbs are your friends in weight loss.",
