    "descriptionPlain": "You should know about this!\nDo you love juices? If yes, watch this!\n\"Eat your vegetables without leaving any on your plate!”\n“Have a fruit and go to play.”\nAlways a piece of advice passed on from generations.\n?? Is it because juices have more calories, or are harmful?\nNo!\n?? When you have a plate of salad, your hunger pangs are curbed for quite some time...\n?? This is because of its high fiber content, which leaves you full for a long time, maintains your blood sugar levels and aiding weight loss.\n?? A glass of juice, on the other hand, can get you hungry in a very short time, causing an instant spike in blood sugar levels.",
