    "descriptionPlain": "A weight loss plateau is when your weight stops dropping despite following the same diet, exercise routine, or lifestyle changes that were previously working. Your body adapts over time, and the initial strategies become less effective.\n\nYou may be in a plateau if:\nYour weight hasn’t changed for 2–4 weeks\n\nHow to Break a Weight Loss Plateau.\nSlightly reduce calories\nIncrease Activity\nImprove Sleep & Reduce Stress\nIncrease Protein Intake",
