    "descriptionPlain": "Click here to find out!\n\r\nMost of us associate Avocados with health & weight loss.\nHowever, on the contrary, Avocado is high in calories & high in fat.\n1 whole medium Avocado contains about 240 calories, 13 grams of carbohydrates, 3 grams of protein, and 22 grams of fat.\nHence, you need to balance off your calorie & fat intake if you want to add Avocados to your diet.\nTo lose weight, focus on consuming low-calorie, low fat & high volume meals.\nDo not get confused with HEALTHY and LOW CALORIE.",
