    "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dg4wzx8c8/image/upload/v1754559510/social_post/images/pzfppvlkrcqrn7kvy5q7.jpg",
    "descriptionPlain": "Click here to find out!\nWhat exactly are empty calories?\nKhyati Rupani's take\nWhen we consume any food, apart from calories...it has carbohydrates, fat, protein and other micronutrients. These nutrients are extremely important in providing us nourishment. .. 1g protein and carbohydrates give us 4 kcal and 1g fat 9 kcal.\nThere are some foods which have ONLY HARMFUL CALORIES and no other nutrition. The net result of making these foods a part of our daily diet will be weight gain, obesity, diabetes and heart ailments. These are called empty calories\nSABUDANA, table sugar, aerated beverages, candies, candy floss are all empty calories",
    "tags": [
      "Gain Weight"
    ],
