    "descriptionPlain": "Check this.\nWeight gain or being overweight is linked always linked to having a “low metabolism”.\nSimply means burning fewer calories when inactive or at rest.\nHere are a few tips to ensure you boost your metabolism\n1. Exercise daily - Even if it means taking the stairs, walking a small distance instead of driving.\n2. Most Indian adult women and children are found having excess fat but are low on protein. This can change by simple changes in the diet !\n3. Eat enough calories- Yes, that’s right. Eating a diet low in calories for a long time also leads to a sluggish metabolism.\n4. Build Muscle - This doesn’t mean carrying a shredded look or go for body building. All it means is build enough muscle to take care of your body composition.\n5. Chillies - The capsacin here is your best bet to fat burning!\n6. Support thyroid- Having an underperforming thyroid can affect our metabolism. Let’s ensure you get it checked every year.",
